      <description>&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
Tyco_Typhoon wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Just wanted to voice what I believe to be a solution to old world zones leveling from 1-50ish and their low population or low desirability... Well first of all you have to ask yourself, what brings a player to a zone? I would say on the top 3 list, number 1 is the xp. If the zone is good xp it will attract players. What I believe would solve the problem of old world zones (ie, Lake of Ill Omen, Frontier mountians, Karana's, Upper/Lower Guk, and much more) is simply increasing the experience gained in these zones to match other newer zones that give better experience. It would be way cool to go back to lake of ill omen and be able to find a group. Or the oasis of mar... &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I also wanted to get other peoples opinions on this idea and perhaps some idea's of your own. Thanks!&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Or, bring down the experience gained in "experience powerhouses" such as Paludal Caverns. Once you are over 50, you will need to leave the old world anyways and move on to Kunark, Velious, the Planes and beyond. There is plenty of experience hot zones over 50.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Below 50 however, everyone is doing the same-old, same-old.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;1-5: Gloomingdeep Mines.&lt;BR&gt;6-10: Either Crushbone or Blackburrow. &lt;BR&gt;11-15: Crushbone or Kurns Tower.&lt;BR&gt;16-25: Paludal Caverns.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;The levels 1 through 25 are pretty much the same thing for most players. Sometimes slightly dependant on faction (Dark Elves hate Crushbone killing), sometimes dependent on where the player is in the world and whether they want to travel.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;I think part of the problem is the lack of newer, lower level players, and the fact that people that want to level up an alt want to get through the first 30 levels as quickly as they can grind it.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Another factor may be the lack of decent graphics in the old world, but I agree, the main factor that draws people to Crushbone, Kurns, and Paludal Caverns is experience.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;I want people back in Oasis! South Karana aviak hunting! Camping the bandit camps in West Karana! Camping the Orcs in West Commonlands! Derv camps in North Ro!&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Maybe together with revamping some zones for newer graphics, (if at all that happens) they could make the older zones attractive again to visit.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
